n style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">the </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">ageing population</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">, </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">yet</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">as they </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">age</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">they </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">are experiencing</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> many of the </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">LTCs</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> found </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">among </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">the older population</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">, but</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> at a</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> much</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> earlier age</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">.</span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="3" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; list-style-position:inside; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-ind